COMMENT ON COLUMN assessment.qti_packages.validation_status IS 'Whether the platform has checked the package and found it valid, invalid, warning-only, or not yet checked.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN assessment.qti_packages.validation_error_count IS 'How many validation problems were found during import.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN assessment.qti_packages.manifest_path IS 'The location of the package manifest file inside the package.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN assessment.qti_packages.original_file_uri IS 'Where the platform stores the original uploaded package file.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN assessment.qti_packages.imported_at IS 'When the platform received or imported the package.';

COMMENT ON TABLE assessment.qti_assessment_items IS 'One question, task, or prompt plus its response variables, scoring rules, body content, feedback, and accessibility metadata.';
